        "TileImage": "$($repository 5087ab4a-586c-4967-967c-487cc2d17c92).Image",
        "Description": "47. This may be your toughest challenge yet.\r\rYour targets are Dmitry Federov and Melissa M. Adams.\r\rThis assignment constitutes the ultimate Ninja challenge. Once more, you&apos;ll begin your approach in the Ninja outfit, by the Mountain path. Both targets must be eliminated using the Katana only, exclusive to the spawn point. No firearms, or explosives allowed for the ultimate challenge. \r\rYou must remain hidden at all times. No alarms, or evidence found. Precision and restraint are critical. \r\rGL!",
